Chi Hyeon!

6
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:58,370
Heo Joon Jae!

7
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:09,680
I saw the person's face.

8
00:01:13,690 --> 00:01:15,590
Heo Chi Hyeon.

9
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:48,820
Ah, really!

10
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:43,580
Heo Joon Jae, I was scared you were going
to protect me again, but I'm so happy.

11
