00:40:09,690 --> 00:40:10,990
Myeongseong University Hospital

418
00:40:18,130 --> 00:40:20,270
It's snowing.

419
00:40:26,910 --> 00:40:31,310
♬ Why am I looking at her? ♬

420
00:40:31,310 --> 00:40:33,850
Tae Ho. ♬ (Could it be love?) ♬

421
00:40:33,850 --> 00:40:35,850
Yes, Noona. Are you going home?

422
00:40:35,850 --> 00:40:40,720
Yes. ♬ Why do I smile when I see her?♬

423
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:44,760
♬ (Could it be love?) ♬

424
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,590
You're not taking me home?

425
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:48,830
- Should I take you?  - No,

426
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:52,430
I thought you wanted to take me.

427
00:40:52,430 --> 00:40:54,770
Never mind. Then...

428
00:40:54,770 --> 00:40:58,670
♬Why am I like this? Why?♬

429
00:40:58,670 --> 00:41:01,140
I said it's fine.

430
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:02,870
Do whatever you want.

431
00:41:02,870 --> 00:41:06,310
♬Why does my heart keep trembling?♬

432
00:41:06,310 --> 00:41:08,910
The snow is so pretty.

433
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:11,350
It is.

434
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:19,090
I'm being generous.

435
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:23,400
You have to have some proper pictures.
You always get sneak shots.

436
00:41:28,430 --> 00:41:29,700
What the heck?

437
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:32,970
Aren't all of these pictures of Cheong?

438
00:41:34,210 --> 00:41:37,080
Come here you!

439
00:41:37,140 --> 00:41:44,750
So the one you liked was not me but Cheong?
Was that it?

440
00:41:44,820 --> 00:41:46,620
Then why did you confess that you liked me?

441
00:41:46,620 --> 00:41:48,850
The thing is... There was some situation...

442
00:41:48,850 --> 00:41:55,130
What? Then what did I do all this time? Did I put
on a show by myself? Why didn't you tell me?

443
00:41:55,230 --> 00:42:00,430
Was it fun seeing me like that? I didn't
even know you were playing with me,

444
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:03,470
I was concerned that you might
get hurt since you liked me.

445
00:42:03,470 --> 00:42:06,540
I was even considering accepting your heart—

446
00:42:25,720 --> 00:42:28,930
I told you not to follow me!

447
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:55,690
I'm sorry.

448
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:59,160
I'm sorry, Noona.

449
00:43:07,430 --> 00:43:16,140
♬ It becomes clear now.
That everything will be for the two of us ♬

450
00:43:16,140 --> 00:43:23,180
♬ Once more was not accidental. ♬

451
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:29,520
♬ Forever we had to meet. ♬

452
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:35,090
The area of the injury stopped
bleeding so I checked the wound, but

453
00:43:35,090 --> 00:43:37,430
there was nothing to bandage.

454
00:43:37,430 --> 00:43:38,710
That's nonsense.

455
00:43:38,920 --> 00:43:42,200
Are you sure you didn't see wrong? How could a
bullet wound disappear that quickly?

456
00:43:42,200 --> 00:43:45,270
But then, now the doctors who were in
the operating room are dumbfounded too.

457
00:43:45,270 --> 00:43:46,920
At first, the bleeding was excessive.

458
00:43:46,920 --> 00:43:48,710
Everyone was nervous, just in case
the aorta (main artery) was ruptured.

459
00:43:48,710 --> 00:43:51,180
But, it's completely clean without even a wound.

460
00:43:51,240 --> 00:43:54,650
Really? What is this? It's scary.

461
00:43:54,650 --> 00:43:58,250
Perhaps, is it something like that? Alien?

462
00:43:58,250 --> 00:43:59,250
That's going a bit far.

463
00:43:59,250 --> 00:44:00,850
- Zombie? - Vampire.

464
00:44:00,890 --> 00:44:05,160
Anyway, the Chief said he'll report the
case at the Heart Association and the AHA

465
00:44:05,160 --> 00:44:08,630
and he's really excited about
contributing to the journal.

466
00:44:08,630 --> 00:44:11,300
I think he already contacted a reporter as well.

467
00:44:11,300 --> 00:44:13,830
Oh, are we being broadcast?

468
00:44:13,830 --> 00:44:15,070
Just get to work.

469
00:44:15,070 --> 00:44:16,700
Let's go.

470
00:44:22,440 --> 00:44:24,640
Are you alright?

471
00:44:33,620 --> 00:44:37,620
- Hello. Did you get the pass to get out? - Yes.

472
00:44:39,420 --> 00:44:41,990
Make sure to take your medication.

