00:45:32,080 --> 00:45:35,950
- Go home ?  - Yeah.

481
00:45:46,630 --> 00:45:48,830
Hey, Upstair's Room.

482
00:45:52,900 --> 00:45:58,040
- What is it?  - Well,
I've been thinking, when Mom moves in,

483
00:45:58,140 --> 00:46:03,540
I think she needs to use this room. Then I don't
have a room, even though I'm the home owner.

484
00:46:03,540 --> 00:46:09,920
So, I think you and I should
share the loft together.

485
00:46:09,920 --> 00:46:12,920
But, when I thought about it,

486
00:46:12,920 --> 00:46:17,860
I wondered if there was a need
to wait until Mom moved here.

487
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:20,690
Right? Should I go up?

488
00:46:20,690 --> 00:46:21,790
No.

489
00:46:21,790 --> 00:46:25,830
So I should. I'll go up.

490
00:46:36,040 --> 00:46:41,780
How long ago was it when you barged down here
and stayed with me when I told you not to come?

491
00:46:41,780 --> 00:46:44,020
She's changed.

492
00:46:55,160 --> 00:47:01,270
♬  Although I can't tell you everything ♬

