00:47:32,760 --> 00:47:35,570
I'll see you often. It's not that far away either.

499
00:47:35,570 --> 00:47:39,200
This is your son's place?
Your son lives in a nice home.

500
00:47:39,240 --> 00:47:44,240
Thanks for dropping me off here.
