00:48:06,430 --> 00:48:08,430
What are you saying?

505
00:48:08,430 --> 00:48:13,610
Ah, this is why I can't trust
you and leave business to you.

506
00:48:13,610 --> 00:48:16,170
Let's go. To Cheonghae's heir's house.
(reference to Lee Min Ho's drama, Heirs)

507
00:48:18,240 --> 00:48:23,820
Unni! You left this at our place.
