519
00:49:03,190 --> 00:49:06,990
I lost track of things and didn't even say hello.

520
00:49:06,990 --> 00:49:09,360
Then, will you do so? Stay and have a cup of tea.

521
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:13,100
Oh, Unni. Why are you being like this? I'll do it.

522
00:49:13,100 --> 00:49:16,370
- Ah, the guest shouldn't do this. Sit.  - Oh no.

