00:49:18,240 --> 00:49:21,110
I asked you to fix it last time!

525
00:49:21,110 --> 00:49:25,040
- You're the one who didn't fix it for me!
- So I'm telling you to fix it yourself!

526
00:49:28,750 --> 00:49:31,820
Goo Baek's Dad!

527
00:49:31,820 --> 00:49:34,190
Jay Kim?

