532
00:49:56,270 --> 00:50:00,150
I didn't know they would come to our home. But
why did Cheong take those people into that room?

533
00:50:00,150 --> 00:50:02,210
It will be fine.

534
00:50:03,020 --> 00:50:05,450
Where did the guests go?

535
00:50:05,450 --> 00:50:07,450
Momentarily...

536
00:50:09,090 --> 00:50:12,560
Oh my. Why are they coming out of the room?

537
00:50:12,560 --> 00:50:17,900
No, we were just looking at the room.
This place is so nice.

538
00:50:19,230 --> 00:50:21,830
Oh my, is this your son?

539
00:50:21,830 --> 00:50:25,270
Yes, my son Heo Joon Jae is here.

540
00:50:25,270 --> 00:50:27,910
This man is his friend, Jo Nam Doo.

541
00:50:27,910 --> 00:50:29,310
And you have been introduced to Cheong, right?

542
00:50:29,310 --> 00:50:32,910
Yes, we have. This young lady is so friendly.

543
00:50:32,910 --> 00:50:36,720
Your son is so handsome.

544
00:50:36,720 --> 00:50:42,050
And, his friend, too... so unique.

545
00:50:43,560 --> 00:50:49,030
But... I...think I have seen you somewhere before.

546
00:50:49,060 --> 00:50:52,900
Your faces feel very familiar.

547
00:50:52,900 --> 00:50:56,770
We met before, right? Dubai?

548
00:50:58,070 --> 00:51:00,770
We've never been to Dubai.

549
00:51:00,770 --> 00:51:02,740
Oh my! Right!

550
00:51:02,740 --> 00:51:08,510
But why did the three syllable word Du-ba-ee
(Dubai in Korean) appear in my head?

551
00:51:12,420 --> 00:51:14,320
I wonder why.

552
00:51:15,390 --> 00:51:18,120
I'm sorry. I'm babbling on.

553
00:51:18,120 --> 00:51:20,530
Anyway, it's so nice to meet you,

554
00:51:20,530 --> 00:51:25,200
and let's meet each other often now.

555
00:51:29,500 --> 00:51:31,940
Think carefully.

556
00:51:31,940 --> 00:51:38,780
Cheong isn't made for mermaid shows!
She erased her memory!

557
00:51:40,180 --> 00:51:42,440
You erased my memories last time too!

558
00:51:42,440 --> 00:51:45,120
And that was why Joon Jae was acting
like that after returning from Spain.

559
00:51:45,120 --> 00:51:47,320
Just try saying this out loud somewhere.

560
00:51:47,320 --> 00:51:52,520
Cheong, let's work together. If you
can use this memory erasing skill well,

561
00:51:52,520 --> 00:51:55,890
we're just applying Bill Gates.
We just become worldwide billionaires.

562
00:51:55,890 --> 00:52:00,470
Don't bother. I won't be a billionaire.
It will make me uselessly busy.

563
00:52:00,470 --> 00:52:03,070
If I'm busy, I won't have time to see Heo Joon Jae.

564
00:52:03,070 --> 00:52:04,900
That's right.

565
00:52:04,900 --> 00:52:08,310
Cheong, I'm saying this sincerely. If you break
up with Joon Jae, you have to come to me.

566
00:52:08,310 --> 00:52:10,710
I pulled number 2, okay?

567
00:52:10,710 --> 00:52:12,180
What is this rascal saying?

568
00:52:12,180 --> 00:52:16,520
Ah, really. Cheong. I really, really
like you. Why do you have so many things?

569
00:52:16,520 --> 00:52:18,820
Hey!

570
00:52:18,820 --> 00:52:20,090
Hey, don't do that.

571
00:52:20,090 --> 00:52:21,450
- Just one time. - Don't do it.

572
00:52:21,450 --> 00:52:24,860
- Just one hug. - Why are you hugging her?

573
00:52:24,860 --> 00:52:26,260
Cheong. Wait.

574
00:52:26,260 --> 00:52:28,660
Hey, what are you doing?

575
00:52:29,730 --> 00:52:32,160
He must be insane.

576
00:52:33,000 --> 00:52:35,570
What's the matter? Why? Cheong?

577
00:52:35,570 --> 00:52:38,500
What's wrong? Are you hurting somewhere?

578
00:52:38,500 --> 00:52:41,570
Hey, maybe you got discharged
from the hospital too soon.

579
00:52:41,570 --> 00:52:43,580
Does your heart hurt?

580
00:52:59,360 --> 00:53:05,800
♬ The door to a new world is open. ♬

