00:54:53,610 --> 00:54:55,940
Shall we have a drink?

600
00:54:56,810 --> 00:54:58,440
No.

601
00:54:59,540 --> 00:55:06,120
If I drink, I think I'll ask you to stay.

602
00:55:09,590 --> 00:55:12,320
If there's another way, tell me.

603
00:55:14,730 --> 00:55:19,870
Please. Tell me there is one.

604
00:55:23,070 --> 00:55:25,900
Since your surgery, you barely eat.

605
00:55:25,900 --> 00:55:30,510
You can't sleep and you hold in your pain.

606
00:55:30,510 --> 00:55:36,480
What am I supposed to do?
Must I continue like this

607
00:55:38,550 --> 00:55:41,850
just watching you die?

608
00:56:06,180 --> 00:56:11,620
If you return to the sea, will you be okay?

609
00:56:13,590 --> 00:56:15,890
Will you be healthy?

610
00:56:31,670 --> 00:56:34,070
Promise me one thing.

611
00:56:35,310 --> 00:56:40,150
That as you are leaving,
you won't erase my memories.

612
00:56:43,150 --> 00:56:44,720
Why?

613
00:56:46,420 --> 00:56:49,220
You said it, too.

614
00:56:49,220 --> 00:56:52,070
Rather than unable to love because
you can't remember,

615
00:56:52,990 --> 00:56:55,690
