616
00:56:56,800 --> 00:57:02,700
Because there will be memories I
share with you, I can let you go.

617
00:57:03,770 --> 00:57:10,280
Then you become too pitiable. I might
not be able to come back for a lifetime.

618
00:57:11,110 --> 00:57:14,780
