619
00:57:15,680 --> 00:57:18,520
You will have to continue to wait.

620
00:57:20,420 --> 00:57:26,290
If you cannot come back for a
lifetime, I'll be born again.

621
00:57:27,660 --> 00:57:30,100
You do that as well.

622
00:57:30,100 --> 00:57:32,100
I told you.

623
